11:
How can we select only these img tag?

12:
We could make a new class called "paragraph-img" and style that class.
("paragraph-img" adında yeni bir sınıf oluşturabilir ve bu sınıfa stil verebiliriz.)

13:
OR we could select only the <img> tags that are inside of <p> tags.
VEYA sadece <p> etiketlerinin içindeki <img> etiketlerini seçebiliriz.

We can only select <img> tags inside the <p> tag, apply a CSS style to them.

14:
CSS Combinators combine two simple selectors to make more specific selector.

15:
We will be looking at 3 combinators:
	-Descendant(dîsendınt) selectors(space)(If we use descendant selector, we should use space.)
	-Child selector (>) (If we use child selector, we should use greater than.)
	-Next Sibling selector (+) (If we use Next Sibling selector, we should use + sign.)


